## 4. Proposed Folder Structure (Separate Workspaces)

```text
📁 Downloads/
├── 📁 MrGardenr v1 Draft/  (Your CURRENT main website - Untouched)
│
└── 📁 MrGardenr_CMS/       (The NEW CMS Workspace)
    ├── 📁 frontend/        (The React/Vite Admin UI)
    │   ├── src/pages/      (Login, Dashboard, Media Manager)
    │   └── src/components/ (UI elements)
    └── 📁 backend/         (The Custom Node.js Auth & API Server)
        ├── controllers/    (Auth logic, Content logic)
        ├── models/         (Database schemas: User, BlogPost)
        └── routes/         (API endpoints)
```

